channel.title: Amethyst. (Zeph Remix) -Tsunan’z [EDM Trap, Bass, Dark]
channel.description:
Here we go! Finally, after a month of debating and composing, I finished it. Hopefully you guys enjoy it as much as I did making it. And shoutout to @Tsunanz for an awesome foundation. I know, even if I dedicated so much time to it, it won’t be perfect, and most of you might not like it. But the reason I keep making music is because I can express my soul through sound. And even if I can’t make a living off of it in the future, it will never stop being my hobby. As always, thanks for listening! -Zeph
[Tsunan’z - amethyst. (Zeph Remix)](https://soundcloud.com/zephprod/tsunanz-amethyst-zeph-remix)
